data.description: Welcome to 5185 Maybury Pl, a charming three-bedroom, one-bathroom home nestled in the heart of Columbus, Ohio. This beautifully maintained home features an open floor plan with 1,239 square feet of living space. The spacious kitchen features stainless steel appliances and a perfect for casual dining. The generously sized master suite offers a walk-in closet and and ensuite bathroom. Outside, you'll find a large backyard perfect for entertaining.This home is located in a community with great amenities. Enjoy close proximity to local schools, shopping centers, parks, and more. Don't miss out on this fantastic opportunity to own a home in Columbus Ohio
